          <a href="#cta-final" class="btn-ghost mt-6 w-full text-center">Começar grátis</a>
          <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--color-primary-base)"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg> Até 3 projetos ativos</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--color-primary-base)"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg> Geração de variações ilimitada</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--color-primary-base)"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg> Renderização 1080p</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="var(--color-primary-base)"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg> Suporte por email</li>
